ğŸ”— Backend API Endpoints

Endpoint	Description

GET /search?meal=Pasta	Search meal by name

GET /categories	Fetch all categories

GET /meals?category=Seafood	Get meals under a category

GET /meal/{id}	Get full meal details

GET /random	Fetch a random meal

